---

<CalculatorPageTemplate
	title="Custody Percentage Calculator"
	description="Estimate custody percentage and parenting time from overnights, days, and custody schedule patterns."
	slug="custody-percentage-calculator"
	lede="Use the custody percentage calculator to understand how many overnights each parent has and how that translates into parenting time percentages."
